{"word":"ἀλλοπρόσαλλος","slug":"ἀλλοπρόσαλλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n4489\" key=\"a)llopro/sallos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀλλο-πρόσαλλος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, i.e. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄλλοτε πρὸς ἄλλον</foreign>, <sense id=\"n4489.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">leaning first to one side, then to the other, fickle</tr_>, epith. of Ares, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:831\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.831</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:889\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">889</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2050.tlg001:p.496\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eun.\">Eun.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ VS\">VS</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.496</biblScope> </bibl> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πλοῦτος</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.12</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.34</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Agath.\">Agath.</a></author> </bibl>); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ ἀ.</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">respect of persons, Corp. Herm.</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4024.tlg001:18:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.14</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n4489.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> simply, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">transferred</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ἀρωγή</foreign>, coupled with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑτεραλκέα νίκην</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0647.tlg001.perseus-grc1:565\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tryph.\">Tryph.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">565</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">deceitful</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:46:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Nonn.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">46.4</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">changeful, successive</tr_>, of waves, etc. (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλεπάλληλος</foreign>), ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2045.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.24</biblScope></bibl>, al., cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2583.tlg001:5:68\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Man.\">Man.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.68</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}